The goal with this bike is really to start making full sus frames using
primarily steel/ stainless steel. I've decided to start with full sus as
I already own a hardtail and don't necessarily need another.

This V1 frame is based on the starling mini murmur

The parts price/link breakout is here: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Qfk6l3psKUX1f9GEHReZujL-EJ3U7GY4GE1FZFarmVs/edit?usp=sharing

UDH Standards: https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&source=web&rct=j&opi=89978449&url=https://www.universalderailleurhanger.com/downloads/90-7518-190-000_E9_RELEASED.pdf&ved=2ahUKEwjJko-Fk5SUAxUFHoYAHecPOc4QFnoECBkQAQ&usg=AOvVaw2pLhz2iYE8iSHL04YZFwTT

Full Frame Specs: https://www.sram.com/globalassets/document-hierarchy/frame-fit-specifications/mtb/2024-mtb-frame-fit-specifications.pdf
